      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB800    BEGSR
      *
     C                     CALL 'DATR10'
     C                     PARM           PDATE   8
     C                     PARM           PRTN    1
      *
     CSR         ESB800    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * CHECK  BLANK PATH-THRU                             *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB810    BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVEL'0'       GET     1
     C                     MOVELD1BHN1    #KSHN1
     C                     MOVELD1BHN2    #KSHN2
     C                     MOVELD1BHN3    #KSHN3
     C                     MOVELP1SEKB    #KSEKB
     C           KEYM11    CHAINMRAPL011             20
     C           *IN20     IFEQ '0'
     C           M1SKJY    ANDEQ'D'
     C           M1SKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     SETON                     20
     C                     ENDIF
     C           *IN20     IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVEL'1'       GET
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     CSR         ESB810    ENDSR
      *
**
ER-1 INPUT CUSTOMER PART NO.
ER-2 INPUT CUSTOMER NAME.
ER-3 INPUT DATE.
ER-4 DATE ERROR.
ER-5 INPUT Y OR N.
ER-6 INPUT COMPLETE PART NO.
ER-7 INPUT BLANK PART NO.
ER-8 CAN'T INPUT PAST DATE.
ER-9 MASS PRODUCTION DATE MUST BE AFTER TOOL ORDER DATE.
ER-10 INPUT QUANTITY.
ER-11 THIS BLANK PART NO ALREADY REGISTED.
